# Real World Scenario

## Situation

A Linux administrator receives a complaint that users cannot access company websites.

Investigation shows:

- Internet connectivity is available.
- DNS resolution fails.

Administrator verifies:

```bash
cat /etc/resolv.conf
```

Tests DNS:

```bash
nslookup google.com
```

Incorrect DNS server configuration is identified and corrected.

Service restored.

